{
  "stem": "16163.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nobody could be on the streets and et cetera, so they had to make sure that nobody was on the streets.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If [? they ?] caught somebody, they would be arrested form the ghetto [? worker, ?] and then the SS would take over, et cetera.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They didn't have an easy task either, because it was like a Jew against Jew.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they really, really tried-- most of 'em-- tried to be good, but it wasn't easy.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From the ghetto [? worker, ?] no.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not really.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No, I really-- personally, I didn't really know anybody, you know, by name [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, it was all surrounded with the-- a lot of uniformed SS with guns.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Wherever you went, there-- you know, you run into somebody in uniform.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And especially when we went out of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this was our life there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I know that there was a resistance in Theresienstadt.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were two resistance--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--groups.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One was the-- called-- was Shalomo-- Shalom, Shalomo, which was a tiny part of the resistance.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And one was the Czeco, and that was for Czech Communists, the Left organization.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I personally knew some people who were in there, but I don't like to mention the name.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "One of them, I know, is in New York, a friend of ours, but I don't want to mention their name.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I spoke to him the other day to find a little more about-- out about it, and he is going in November to Theresien by invitation from the Czech government and the ghetto organizations there still in the museum.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he's going to give a lecture from the real inside of the resistance, which a lot of people don't even know about that it was going on.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
